org.dllearner.kb.sparql.query
Class SparqlQuery

java.lang.Object
  org.dllearner.kb.sparql.query.SparqlQuery

public class SparqlQuery
extends Object

Represents one SPARQL query. It includes support for stopping the SPARQL query (which may be necessary if a timeout is reached).

Author:
Jens Lehmann
